==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Muzzy
<hw>Muz"zy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>muse</ets>.]</ety> <def>Absent-minded; dazed; muddled;
stupid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The whole company stared at me with a whimsical, <qex>muzzy</qex>
look, like men whose senses were a little obfuscated by beer rather than
wine.</q> <rj><qau>W. Irving.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>MVP</ent>⟦br⟧
